own.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T12:34:27.000Z","msg":"少到台灣人search av keyword 係貧乳<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T12:38:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/1-30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F1-30.jpg&h=3d606622&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本成人漫畫網站 Komiflo 最近公開了「2020年版都道府県」人氣類別，同時也收錄了香港、台灣和新加坡等會員的觀看偏好，而其中香港搜尋類別人氣最高的是「人妻」，「JK」和「寝取」。<br />\n<br />\nKomiflo 網站慣例每年都會公佈旗下會員最喜愛的關鍵字類別，其中不但包含了日本 47 個都道府縣區域的觀衆偏好，香港和台灣觀衆的搜尋偏好也包含在裏面。而最新公佈的 2020 年數據中，香港區域搜尋類別人氣最高分別為「人妻」，「JK (女高中生)」和「寝取 NTR」。而上年最受歡迎的「癡女」系列則被擊敗。而台灣排名前三分別為「貧乳」，「JK」和「人妻」。類別人氣的不同也顯示了各國風俗民情的分別。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Ezp1iNLVcAkuZws.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2FEzp1iNLVcAkuZws.jpeg&h=8692f0de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/3-13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F3-13.jpg&h=c575f086&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/2-23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F2-23.jpg&h=3d761383&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://twitter.com/komiflo/status/1385549069104291840?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkomiflo%2Fstatus%2F1385549069104291840%3Fs%3D20&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOG6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=a914b23a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkomiflo%2Fstatus%2F1385549069104291840%3Fs%3D20&h=2a2d6bd6\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/komiflo/status/1385549069104291840?s=20</a><br />\n\t<br />\nKomiflo 指出，2019 年時網站使用者的男女比例約為 9 比 1，到 2020 年尾比例變為 8 比 2。由於 Komiflo 平台的使用人數無法準確計算，因此提供的數據僅供參考。"},{"pid":"6883b756ddd69856fe78d54b8858edea60b62cca","tid":2514700,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T12:39:31.000Z","msg":"集集都大波妹架喇<br />\n台妹標配"},{"pid":"8a4521672cdae0c81fad17673ea81e960a5fad1a","tid":2514700,"uid":71632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T12:41:12.000Z","msg":"佢D片全部都係model公司搵佢拍嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n扮素人等D傻仔推佢上位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e6e401a3971e866011e068a7ede6809cbc3ea7d","tid":2514700,"uid":232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a4521672cdae0c81fad17673ea81e960a5fad1a","tid":2514700,"uid":71632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T12:41:12.000Z","msg":"佢D片全部都係model公司搵佢拍嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n扮素人等D傻仔推佢上位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T12:42:25.000Z","msg":"都要有咁多大波model先得㗎"},{"pid":"58e9cf0b0c1c2c772e465c9d4b7626f4ad20e19b","tid":2514700,"uid":384590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T12:43:06.000Z","msg":"好多業配<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ab5b7f42bdef2fde54fd8ee019ef89b175e5820","tid":2514700,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f53df09d66377ae9a5936a6838da1b3feba90d0b","tid":2514700,"uid":7828,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ff008f88f9d1f3b2883a580d713906136ed2230a","tid":2514700,"uid":155559,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6070f85dd150d22539bf77688a4b3e8289f39cef","tid":2514700,"uid":71433,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T12:14:39.000Z","msg":"台灣有飛機場咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T12:34:27.000Z","msg":"少到台灣人s